fields.Action:
1. Initiate a CWMP session
	2. The ACS sends a GetParameterValues request using the root node as the partial path: InternetGatewayDevice.

	If the TR-181 is supported:

	Device.
fields.Expected Result: To be successful the device must either return a GetParameterValuesResponse message containing the parameter values for each complete path parameter in the object model or return an appropriate SOAP fault. Fault 9004 would be nice to see, although many devices seem to return 9002.

fields.description: The purpose of this test is to validate that a device can return values for all of the parameters in the object model in a single RPC request.
